{"word":"G1089 - γεύομαι - geúomai - ghyoo'-om-ahee - Eat","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γεύομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">geúomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ghyoo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Eat</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ருசிபார், புசி, சாப்பிடு"},{"paragraph":"to cause to taste, to give one a taste of"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to <i>taste</i>; by implication to <i>eat</i>; figuratively to <i>experience</i> (good or ill): - eat, taste.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}